text: Cum Cake is the debut mixtape from American hip hop artist Cupcakke. It was released on February 9, 2016 independently through TuneCore. The first single, "Vagina", was released on October 9, 2015. "Deepthroat" and "Juicy Coochie" were later-released singles along with "Tit for Tat", "Exceptions", and "Pedophile". The mixtape was listed in Rolling Stones December 2016 40 Best Rap Albums of 2016. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:Cupcakke albums Category:2016 mixtape albums
